OL,6,FA man has been charged with preventing
OL,7,Fa lawful burial after a body was found
OL,8,Fin a freezer, ITV News understands.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police were called to an
OL,11,Faddress in Poplar Crescent in
OL,12,FPorthcawl at around 1.45pm on Tuesday
OL,13,F17 February after reports about the
OL,14,Fwelfare of a woman.
OL,16,FThe body of woman in her 80s was found
OL,17,Fdead at the property.
